Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去解開鳴人和鹿丸的幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒執行任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要當心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是繼波之國之後的A級任務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明也會反彈幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎還裝睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追蹤佐助 與他會合併阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新的命令下達之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個安全的地方待命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳情邊走邊說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情演變成這樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助那個傢伙 幹嗎那麼急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 為什麼連我也要來追蹤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩極了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是卡卡西老師的命令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概要多久才能追上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也在以極快的速度移動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑第一 雖然麻煩也必須面對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度再快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是找到佐助了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面有兩個小隊 八個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有九個人在追我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有追兵了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來對方還沒掌握到確切的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 照做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿著我們的腳印像這樣倒退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳印就會像突然消失一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後他們還是會發現的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以多爭取一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓追兵焦躁 不知從何追起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後失去線索就謝天謝地了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說我也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經做了偽裝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們仍在逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕都是中忍以上的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被追上可就全軍覆沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍覆沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們乾脆打個伏擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏擊對我們有利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算對方比我們人多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能打他們個措手不及的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方可是前木葉忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好還有上忍在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以為行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋伏和對手的等級沒什麼關聯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個根本不懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏擊確實是一種有利的基本戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但必須具備兩個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼條件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走的一方必須悄無聲息地行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並能先一步發現敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出能夠打得對手措手不及
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且確實能攻擊到對方要害的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速埋伏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有具備這兩個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏擊才會成為一個有利的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一點有忍犬的鼻子應該不難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於第二點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我們的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們熟悉地形好像很有利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大蛇丸也是前木葉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對其部下這招就不管用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底有什麼結論嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他們非常瞭解村子的地形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時為了這次行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能做過多次模擬演習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:08:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外他們都是精通追蹤術的忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們已經被他們吃透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏擊是有利的戰術是不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不確定因素太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信敵人是為了這次的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組成了特別部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反觀我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有特殊優點的女忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一隻狗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑第一的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰略這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是詳細掌握現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後擬定出最佳對策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在能做的只有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是假裝伏擊的誘敵戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留一個人假裝我們要伏擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他們的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就無法掌握其他三人的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣追蹤就無法繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過當誘餌的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那誰去當誘餌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要這隻狗幫我們追蹤佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來總比全軍覆沒好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既能成功誘敵 又可能活下來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅長影子模仿術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是為了阻止敵人行動的忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會追上你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交給你了 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到鹿丸這麼可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎麼隱藏足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是破綻百出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人離我們越來越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真去牽制敵人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑第一的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…鹿丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸絕對沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他該不會趁機逃跑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說他不會有問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙的嘴巴雖然很壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且怕麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他絕不會背叛夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他很少主動上前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他一定會說到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然很想相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加快速度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算順利逃出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步伐混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他們開始焦慮疲憊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我應該走為上策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這次我的角色不太一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然疲憊是沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那些腳印是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是狗腳印的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 還是個小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我們被這種小鬼困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:14:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳聞中的木葉的影子束縛術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種說法太古老了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時代的潮流在改變哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在叫做影子模仿術了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來那場比賽果然有影響
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的查克拉消耗太多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計撐不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5 6 7 8
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有九個人在追我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來第九個人的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是保護這八個追蹤者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們保持一定的距離 在後方移動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以應敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我這麼做 就知道他躲在哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子沒辦法伸到那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒有體力運用查克拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經看穿了你的技倆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你已經到達極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這招影子模仿術馬上就會解除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:15:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來打算隨便做個忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便賺點錢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後娶一個不美也不醜的普通女人當老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便生兩個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一胎是個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二胎是個男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等長女結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒子也能獨當一面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就從忍者圈退休
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後過一天算一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下下將棋或圍棋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過著悠然自得的隱居生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後比自己的老婆早一步老死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我心目中的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我卻出來搶風頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想普普通通過完一生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果越搞越麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤我們的人已經停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功牽制敵人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鹿丸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才居然懷疑你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 我們馬上到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對要活著追上我們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便把這傢伙的腦袋砍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總算追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯瑪 怎麼會是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸 這次你表現得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然不適合做這些事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面你就可以休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙還真煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵增加了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勘九郎 再加快點速度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要操之過急啊 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.56,0:22:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎麼搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.90,0:22:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼火影爺爺會跟大蛇丸交手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助為什麼會去追那個黑眼圈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要阻止佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也只能繼續追了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我等等啊 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.12,0:23:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古今無雙 火影級的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.14,0:23:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子到底會怎樣呢
